Hello peeps!

Do you get really pained when you work hard for your performance and then
can't control what happens onstage?

Why is this workshop important?
LitSoc LM and WM Group are happening on the 16th, 17th of April and
this session will get you better equipped to get good sound on stage and
learn about lights!

Meet your instructor
Mike Williams is the proprietor of Audio Sciences  an acoustic solutions
company and has arranged sound and lights for Benny Dayal, Bombay Jayshree
as well as music events at Saarang and LitSoc. He brings in a dual
perspective, being both a musician and a sound engineer.

He will be handling sound for WM, LM Group this year.

Help us decide the content!
Now you know Mike's background, please fill in this form
 with any questions that you'd like
answered in the session.  We'll try to accommodate your suggestions.

Thank you!
Cheers,
Prakruti (9043412827)
Harish   (9445404148)

 
